import React from 'react'
import { View, Text,StyleSheet } from 'react-native'
import NavBar from "../components/NavBar"

const CartScreen = () => {
    return (
        <View style={{flex:1}}>
            <NavBar/>
            <View >
            <Text >Cart</Text>
            </View>
        </View>
    )
}



export default CartScreen
